---
import CalendlyButton from "./CalendlyButton.astro";
---

<footer id="site-footer" class="mt-24 pb-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-[url('/images/footer-bg.png')] bg-cover bg-center"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/35 backdrop-blur-[1px]"></div>

      <div class="relative px-6 pt-20 pb-8 md:px-10 md:pt-28">
        <a
  href="#top"
  class="footer-scroll-link"
  aria-label="Retour en haut de page"
>
  ↑
</a>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-[var(--brown-deep)]">
            Prendre soin de soi, c’est se donner la possibilité de vivre plus aligné et plus serein.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 soft-card rounded-t-[2.5rem] rounded-b-none p-8 md:p-10">
          <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_0.8fr_0.9fr]">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
              
              <img
  src="/images/alexandra-coirier.webp"
  alt="Alexandra Coirier, sophrologue à Loudéac"
  class="h-60 w-40 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg"
/>

              <div>
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)]">
                  Alexandra Coirier
                </p>

                <p class="mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--brown-soft)]">
                  Sophrologue à Loudéac
                </p>

                <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-[var(--text)]">
                  J’accompagne les personnes qui traversent une période de stress,
                  d’anxiété, de fatigue, de surcharge mentale ou de transition de vie.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-6">
<CalendlyButton
            label="Prendre rendez-vous"
            className="px-6 py-3"
            url="https://calendly.com/alexandracoirier-sophrologue/?hide_gdpr_banner=1&primary_color=9a6750&text_color=5e4a42&background_color=f8f2ef"
          />  </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)]">
                Navigation
              </p>

              <nav class="mt-5 grid gap-3 text-[var(--text)]">
                <a href="/" class="footer-link">Accueil</a>
                <a href="/a-quoi-s-attendre" class="footer-link">À quoi s’attendre</a>
                <a href="/accompagnement" class="footer-link">Accompagnements</a>
                <a href="/mon-approche" class="footer-link">Mon approche</a>
                <a href="/qui-suis-je" class="footer-link">Qui suis-je ?</a>
                <a href="/faq" class="footer-link">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="footer-link">Contact</a>
              </nav>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)]">
                Informations
              </p>

              <div class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-[var(--text)]">
                <p>
                  <a href="tel:+33781528517" class="footer-link">
                    07 81 52 85 17
                  </a>
                </p>

                <p>
                  <a
                    href="mailto:contact@alexandracoirier-sophrologue.fr"
                    class="footer-link break-all"
                  >
                    contact@alexandracoirier-sophrologue.fr
                  </a>
                </p>

                <p>
                  26 Rue du Dr Robin<br />
                  22600 Loudéac
                </p>
              </div>

              <nav class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-sm">
                <a href="/mentions-legales" class="footer-link">Mentions légales</a>
                <a href="/politique-confidentialite" class="footer-link">Politique de confidentialité</a>
                <a href="/politique-cookies" class="footer-link">Politique de cookies</a>
              </nav>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

  <div class="-mt-1 rounded-b-[2.5rem] bg-[var(--brown-deep)]/85 px-6 py-5 md:px-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-white/90">
    <p>
      © 2025 Alexandra Coirier – Sophrologue à Loudéac • Tous droits réservés
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-3">
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/p/Alexandra-Coirier-Sophrologue-100072807305535/" class="footer-social" aria-label="Facebook">f</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/alexandracoirier_sophrologie/" class="footer-social" aria-label="Instagram">◎</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer-link {
    color: var(--text);
    transition: color 220ms ease, transform 220ms ease;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--brown-deep);
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .footer-social {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 220ms ease, background 220ms ease;
  }

  .footer-social:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }

  .footer-scroll-link {
  position: absolute;
  top: 2rem;
  right: 2rem;
  z-index: 20;
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  background: var(--brown-soft);
  color: white;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(94, 74, 66, 0.25);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
}
</style>